@startuml
title Figure 6. DocuTracker User Sequence

actor Employee
actor Reviewer
participant "DocuTracker App" as App
participant "Server" as Server
database Database

== Create and submit ==
Employee -> App : **1.** Create document
App -> Server : **2.** Save draft
Server -> Database : **3.** Store document
Database --> App : **4.** Draft saved

Employee -> App : **5.** Submit for review
App -> Server : **6.** Start workflow
Server -> Database : **7.** Assign reviewer,\nset deadline
Database --> Reviewer : **8.** Notification sent

== Review ==
Reviewer -> App : **9.** Open assigned document
App -> Server : **10.** Request document
Server -> Database : **11.** Fetch record
Database --> App : **12.** Document details

Reviewer -> App : **13.** Approve
App -> Server : **14.** Process approval
Server -> Database : **15.** Update status
Database --> App : **16.** Approved
App --> Employee : **17.** Status updated

@enduml
